BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:First United Church
DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260322T091500
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260322T100000
DTSTAMP:20260317T122642
CREATED:20260216T212047Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260216T212350Z
UID:10012603-1774170900-1774173600@firstuc.org
SUMMARY:Synoptic Gospels Bible Study
DESCRIPTION:Read the Synoptics in a Year \nAs we seek to live out our mission more fully\, you are invited to explore the words and deeds of Jesus through studying the synoptic gospels (Mark\, Matthew\, and Luke) over the course of 2026. This exploration will include daily readings (access suggested reading schedule here)\, a weekly Sunday morning discussion group (9:15-10am in Roger Williams Hall and via Zoom\, click here)\, and weekly sermons during worship. Let us join together in following Jesus more faithfully and fruitfully in this new year!
URL:https://firstuc.org/events/synoptic-gospels-bible-study/2026-03-22/
LOCATION:Roger Williams Hall
CATEGORIES:Education
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:First United Church
DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260322T103000
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260322T113000
DTSTAMP:20260317T122642
CREATED:20260216T212805Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260216T212811Z
UID:10012930-1774175400-1774179000@firstuc.org
SUMMARY:Sunday Morning Hybrid Worship
DESCRIPTION:Sunday Morning Hybrid Worship\nJoin us for worship each Sunday morning at 10:30am. This Sunday’s service will feature Rev. Jessica Petersen-Mutai in the pulpit; she will also offer a special message for the young and young at heart. Be sure to join us in Fellowship Hall after worship for a time of fellowship and refreshment.\nJoin the Zoom Webinar by clicking here \nDial-in number: (312) 626-6799; Webinar ID: 828 3681 0281 \nThe service will be posted on Sunday evening on First United’s Vimeo channel (where you can access all of our previous worship services).
URL:https://firstuc.org/events/sunday-morning-hybrid-worship-4-2-2/2026-03-22/
LOCATION:Sanctuary
CATEGORIES:Community,Fellowship,Worship
END:VEVENT
